			<action-desc>
        <sponsor name-id="S340">Ms. Ayotte</sponsor> (for herself and <cosponsor name-id="S312">Mrs. McCaskill</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the <committee-name committee-id="SSGA00">Committee on Homeland Security and Governmental Affairs</committee-name>
